latestPosts.caption: “Happy birthday, Papa! We love you so, so much! On your special day, we want to take a moment to express how grateful we are to have you in our lives. Your strength, wisdom, kindness, and endless support have shaped us in ways we can never truly repay. You’ve always been there, whether to share a laugh, give advice, or simply be a comforting presence. We admire everything you do for our family, and your love and care never go unnoticed. Thank you for being such an amazing father, role model, and friend. We cherish every moment spent with you and look forward to many more years of love and happiness together. Here’s to celebrating you today and always—Happy Birthday, Papa!”❤️🧿❤️

🎥 Step into the spotlight with our latest reel featuring Managing Director, Mrs. Navneet Kukreja! 🌟 In this captivating video, Mrs. Kukreja shares invaluable insights into the transformative journey our students embark on when they join Lakme Academy Gandhi Nagar, Jammu. 💼👩‍🎓

As Mrs. Kukreja eloquently puts it, our courses are not just about learning makeup, hair, and skincare techniques; they are about grooming the personalities of our students. 🌸💇‍♀️ In our vibrant classroom environment, students learn alongside their peers, soaking in the collective knowledge and experience. This dynamic setting fosters growth and development, nurturing not just their skills, but also their confidence and individuality. 🌟

But that's not all – at Lakme Academy Gandhi Nagar, we go the extra mile to ensure our students receive comprehensive training and exposure. Through seminars, competitions, and extra classes, we provide additional avenues for our students to hone their talents and excel in their craft. 🏆💄 It's not just about learning; it's about earning valuable experiences and opportunities that pave the way for a successful career in the beauty industry. 💼💫

Join us today and experience the transformative power of education at Lakme Academy Gandhi Nagar. 🎓 Don't miss your chance to unleash your potential and embark on a journey of growth and success. Tap the WhatsApp button below for admissions and queries, or call us at 7006626196 / 8130187894. Visit us at House No. 3A Pvt, HK Villa, adjoining UCO bank, Park Electric Lane, Gandhi Nagar, Jammu, Jammu and Kashmir. 🏡
